"{\"uid\": \"dailydot.com-news-flavor-flav-water-polo-paris-olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Mike Hadge  Why is American rapper Flavor Flav at the Paris Olympics and spending time with the USA Water Polo team?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9769924576215184, \"rank\": 0.02354773916748353, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 46, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7217647512989806e-58, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}, {\"begin\": 96, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_water_polo_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999997953637, \"rank\": 2.046042128752586e-10, \"text\": \"USA Water Polo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_water_polo_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_water_polo_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us explain.\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to things that make you go \\\"whaa?\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", theOlympicsare a harvest season of true abundance, a point that's even more driven home by this year's featuring stuff that's extremely, what's the word, French.\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9842055124646715, \"rank\": 0.015907836148442798, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From headless Marie Antoinette metal performances toStranger Things-meets-Phantom of the Operaopening ceremonies, there is no shortage of curios so far at this year's Paris Olympiad.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3603621396479522e-27, \"text\": \"Marie Antoinette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympiad\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, if you have been watching any of the water polo events so far, you may have noticed a recognizable figure who seems lost and, knowing him, very well might have been.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"gotta love Flavor Flav being the official hype man for women's water polopic.twitter.com/uX47qipq4W  Yes, rap legend Flavor Flav has been ever-present at the US polo events.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 717, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7217647512989806e-58, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}, {\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7217647512989806e-58, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}, {\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"score\": 0.9878163810754258, \"rank\": 0.012333582272456218, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have undoubtedly caught a glimpse during the broadcast so far and thought, \\\"wait, should not he be wearing comically large clock necklaces somewhere?\\\"\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Flav's presence is of a more official manner than you might imagine.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's fantastic.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On May 4th, water polo Olympian Maggie Steffens posted onInstagramthat revealed how many Olympic athletes hold second and third jobs to help achieve their medal dreams.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999997129407759, \"rank\": 2.8078051095844515e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1167, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maggie Steffens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Below that post was a comment by Flav, who wrote, \\\"AYYY YOOO,,, as a girl dad and supporter of all women's sports-imma personally sponsor you my girl,,, whatever you need.\\\"\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And imma sponsor the whole team,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My manager is in touch with your agent and imma use all my relationships and resources to help all you all even more.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a FLAVOR FLAV promise.\\\"\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How good is a Flavor Flav promise, you ask?\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As good as its weight in gold clock necklaces, because on July 1st, Flavor Flavofficially signed a five-year sponsorship dealwith USA Water Polo to cover the men's and women's water polo teams.\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Flava Flav is sponsoring the USA Women's water polo team, who's won 3 consecutive Olympic gold medals, so that the team members do not have to keep working multiple jobs just to support themselves while they are also training.pic.twitter.com/0fjrUJcj6K  Flavspoke to NBC Olympics in Mayto explain more of his reasoning behind the support.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1914, \"end\": 1924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Flava Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}, {\"begin\": 1943, \"end\": 1946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.8540164515122755, \"rank\": 0.17093761845153838, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me doing this, I ain't gonna lie, to me this is one of the biggest things that I feel that I could have ever done in life, outside of the other accomplishments that I have made to music,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"By sponsoring a water polo team and helping these girls out, this is bigger than me winning a Grammy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's all pretty awesome and Flav looks like he's having the time of his damn life cheering on the team, encouraging other celebrities to do the same, and evenhanging out withFirst Lady Jill Biden.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2745, \"end\": 2755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Biden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jill Biden\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Biden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Biden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flav's also not content to just cheer from the sidelines.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The man wants in on the action too:  We got Flavor Flav in the pool you all \\ud83d\\udc4f\\ud83c\\udffc  Either way, Flav has garnered a whole lot of goodwill from the gesture.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Including online:  The fact that he became the team's official FIVE-YEAR sponsor after learning about their financial struggles\\u2026almost like listening to women leads to progresshttps://t.co/mhO4ZhYxR6  Love this, Flava Flav is sponsoring the USA Women's Water Polo team after finding out members of the team were quietly working multiple jobs to pay for training and competing even after winning 3 Olympic gold medals.\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3182, \"end\": 3192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Flava Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}, {\"begin\": 3211, \"end\": 3214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.8540164515122755, \"rank\": 0.17093761845153838, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 3223, \"end\": 3233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Water_polo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 1.7300653903862776e-13, \"text\": \"Water Polo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Water_polo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Water_polo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's calling other celebrities to do the same with other teams.\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There must be 100 people waiting for a pic or selfie with Flav, and he's accommodating every single request.pic.twitter.com/9lIb8xpO94  The French gonna French, but the *truly* wild image to emerge from Paris thus far is 65 year-old rapper Flava Flav embracing Jill Biden at women's water polo.The story behind the impromptu Flava Flav-FLOTUS summit is\\u2026 very Flav, and very America:pic.twitter.com/UAbP7pZfr7  #FlavaFlavbeing the official hype man for the women's water polo team is exactly what the world needs.#Olympic2024pic.twitter.com/6XPYBJ6exj  Honestly, they should probably just let him compete.\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 4055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3606, \"end\": 3612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9842055124646715, \"rank\": 0.015907836148442798, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3656, \"end\": 3661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.009559237985834e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3686, \"end\": 3692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hip_hop_music\", \"score\": 0.9566143559683395, \"rank\": 0.04535332734770998, \"text\": \"rapper\", \"types\": [\"Q188451\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hip_hop_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hip_hop_music\"}, {\"begin\": 3693, \"end\": 3703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Flava Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}, {\"begin\": 3714, \"end\": 3724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Biden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jill Biden\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Biden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jill_Biden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just for one competition that they do not really care about.\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Come on, the guy's earned it!\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, Flav is not the only old-school rap icon to be having a blast at the 2024 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 4148, \"to\": 4249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop Dogg's there too folks, providinginterviews and commentaryas only he can.\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop Dogg & FlavaFlav doing more for our image abroad than Trump/Vance ever could.Making America Fun Again!pic.twitter.com/ciXNaLelAo  Your move, Vanilla Ice.\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4393, \"end\": 4398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999217835, \"rank\": 7.812248904231218e-11, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 4399, \"end\": 4404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9999994191654745, \"rank\": 5.807333626373504e-07, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}, {\"begin\": 4480, \"end\": 4491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanilla_Ice\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6049497958006733e-28, \"text\": \"Vanilla Ice\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanilla_Ice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanilla_Ice\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Internet culture is chaotic-but we will break it down for you in one daily email.\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up for the Daily Dot's web_crawlr newsletterhere.\", \"from\": 4576, \"to\": 4630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will get the best (and worst) of the internet straight into your inbox.\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know when the bills will stop\\\": Simpsons fan with \\\"BORT\\\" vanity plate overwhelmed with toll notices  The cute gummy bear Haribo battery everyone wanted is apparently a fire hazard  \\\"Shows how important real actors are\\\": Amazon Prime Video users are canceling their accounts after noticing  AI dubbing in \\\"Banana Fish\\\"  \\\"Even square, it's delicious\\\": Burger King's new Spon